Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:09.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:10.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:15.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Hayate's morning, the day started peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:20.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But he had no clue that this was the start of\Nthe day that would change the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.21,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, how about you visit the main house\Nwhere your grandfather is once in a while? {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.88,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be good to introduce Hayate-kun, too. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.28,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And please don't make that spiteful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this grandfather?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:42.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the Sanzenin family, Grandfather Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Head?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's the current president of the Sanzenin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:53.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then any mistake I make might lead to me being fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:58.44,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, to him, it's easy enough to erase your existence from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:08.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who dedicates himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:14.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.33,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:23.91,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The human body contains a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The more you train...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:13.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's necessary to go say hi to that old man just cause we hired a new butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.11,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He's your only blood relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:23.52,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's been a while since I last met Old Mikado. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:27.18,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. Why are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:30.94,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I'm a relative, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:34.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But, what exactly is your grandfather like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of Dragon **est, he'd be Zo**.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.71,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of comedy show, he'd be the ***.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:43.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I going to survive meeting someone that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.54,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it won't be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:50.49,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,If you displease him, he can easily erase the life of a debt-ridden butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:56.38,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he forced Com**** to bankruptcy because he founded Pu** Pu**.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:04:00.88,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,And for your information,\N********** going down was done by him, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.26,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,She's lying, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:10.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, he's like a half-ghost, so don't get possessed by some strange thing he may say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.12,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:13.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Just to let you know, it's not\NToxic-Apple-Eating-Princess Castle at Mouseland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Sanzenin Mikado-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.88,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Grandfather's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What country are we in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:35.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What does he do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oil baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.19,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:44.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate was coming to an understanding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:47.82,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi wasn't an ordinary rich girl on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.84,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Lady Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:02.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She's a super rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But they're so uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.54,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuya-sama, Maria-dono.\NYou must both be tired from the long travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.56,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.29,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm sorry to interrupt you when you've just returned, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.21,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,...what should we do about this unauthorized individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.22,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He had snuck onto the helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.03,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What a really suspicious-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you mean, but he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He's my new butler who replaced Himegami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:33.70,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This guy who looks like he has no luck with money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.88,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,But... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:47.60,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's absolutely true\Nthat he has no money and a poor-man's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to highlight it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.23,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,But that was hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:57.00,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Saku, don't laugh too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:01.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine; I was aware that I'd come to the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:08.78,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it so personally. They only said what they saw and meant no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. It's only a waste of time to worry over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:16.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do have a 150 million yen debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,but do I appear to be that detached from money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:23.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,A thoughtful mind is more important in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:27.70,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Every individual has to think about the Earth's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,They're avoiding eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:35.57,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Nagi. You can't possibly be in those clothes to meet your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get changed, so you go get some fresh air outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I got kicked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the point in saying this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:59.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it dangerous to let\Na debt-ridden guy like me walk around loose here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.51,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an expensive thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.61,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can repay the entire 150 million yen with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:19.72,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,That vase is only about 5 million yen over Yah** ***tion, so it won't be enough to pay the debt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:36.67,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I can tell by looking at you\Nthat you're not the kind of person who would do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:43.68,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop looking at me with those\N"hey, what's this old fart saying?" eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.94,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.92,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, I'm taking care of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're the landscaper of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.41,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe in my eye, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.80,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.23,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:11.94,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll show you how accurate my eyes are, so follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:16.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,His face is sparkling like that of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.02,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.83,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, these clothes are a little big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's called peeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:39.36,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You need daily training to improve your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:43.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of criminal do you intend to become after all the training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:52.85,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't understand how you ended up\Nwith a debt of 150 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally a debt my parents made from gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:04.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are total losers\Nand gave me as a present to very kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then Lady Nagi paid the debt off for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So right now, I'm in the process of paying her back over the course of forty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:15.13,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to Lady Nagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:22.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,so you shouldn't be doing things like peeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:35.15,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, your life is infinitely worthless, I take it. {hmmm... -Fluff}{Al - "entirely without meaning"?  Really I think "meaningless" captures "muimi" a bit more accurately in this case, in general?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:47.60,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather boring for a man Nagi has laid her eyes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.11,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:59.78,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I've foreseen the economy breaking down,\Nchanges in government, and ****-chan balding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:05.05,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I had even foreseen the younger sister boom coming from before the start of World War Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.89,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And my eyes are telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:12.15,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is even more worthless than those of your trashed parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:17.74,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sanzenin Mikado, will give you my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,My life is worthless?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.56,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:30.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,A life spent to repay a debt is infinitely worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:36.58,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,But if you still wish to make your life worthwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:41.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A levistone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.28,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,NO! That's a guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.80,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,If you think your life is not worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.85,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,then keep that on until\Nthe necessary day comes and do not lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:11:03.02,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And if you can attain what lies beyond its guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:06.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,then forget 150 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.19,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You can gain a trillion or ten trillion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:22.42,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After having his life completely rejected,\Ncan Hayate walk to the wards the pendant guides him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.36,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.60,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Maria! Are we sure we don't need a gag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:33.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, did I ever do any gags before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.86,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.81,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be at least one gag per minute, or else my Kansai blood won't let me be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.95,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away! I can't settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.60,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That form of gag is already old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say this clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.92,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.85,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Land flat on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.19,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.48,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Lambada
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.81,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Dankai no sedai
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.81,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Dankai no sedai = Baby-Boomer Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:13.04,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,My granddaughter. Do you seek the Sanzenin estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:19.05,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need it, but I'd be glad to see you leave this world soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:24.30,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! Maria! My granddaughter is bullying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.92,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what trouble we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not bullying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.73,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, I don't need the estate, so can you give me some cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even without it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:37.69,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I have World Business Satellite\Nand the stock market, I won't have trouble with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.17,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her. She's gaining unnecessary knowledge every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who taught me to gain this knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.06,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.22,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember teaching you to draw a worthless manga like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.01,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get my manga from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.11,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,See, my granddaughter bullies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.13,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:09.73,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Grandfather, why are you bringing this up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.77,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because, at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.71,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I have a winning popsicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this one's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:49.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what my parents were like, I'm always thinking about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I never spared a single thought for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.95,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But, is that really all right with my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:14:00.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A life spent only to pay off debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.47,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.88,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I looked all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.57,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're returning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can't possibly spend any more time with that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:23.17,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, but rather will happen, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So he really came.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:52.38,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good to dodge my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:56.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is this fake foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a long story to tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,but he's someone who might inherit the entire Sanzenin estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Inherit it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:13.10,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The story won't go anywhere if we leave Nagi to do the explanation, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.00,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:17.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just have you watch what happened after we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:22.15,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Grandfather, why are you bringing this up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.16,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because, at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.08,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.87,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why will I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finally developed dementia, old foggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.50,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I have not developed dementia, and I'm not a "foggy" either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.83,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it for a second, my granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.19,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much time ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:46.31,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And when I die, the entire estate will go to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.93,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,but there are many within the family that do not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:55.91,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there are parents out there that would sell their son for 150 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.67,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,so there could be those who may come after Nagi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.17,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.03,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've come to a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:09.41,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,When a certain condition is met,\Nthe estate will be given to this certain person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.88,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. And that condition is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.37,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,And that condition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:27.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I lose. I'll give you all the estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,so please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.07,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Make Nagi cry and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:44.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than utter such embarrassing words!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:50.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me to understand what rich people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I don't understand, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.26,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.36,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Cry and apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.70,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd apologize to you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.73,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please cry and apologize to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.48,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Does he not have any pride at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to do that. Go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:18.92,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then you leave me with no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.69,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:32.56,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,From what old Mikado tells me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:42.54,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,if I beat down that wimpy looking butler,\Nthere's a chance our Lady will cry and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:48.49,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll smack him down and make the estate mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:52.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If Milady can't inherit the Sanzein estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,she won't be as rich as she is anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then that'll make her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She'll end up on the street like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.85,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The porridge is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:12.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for all the trouble, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,We promised not to say that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If only Hayate-kun would pay the money back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:26.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have lent him 150 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.09,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.10,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.87,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:43.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:51.28,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,A life spent to repay the debt is infinitely worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.49,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.54,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:19:00.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, who came to save me wearing such a hilarious mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.23,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, who took care of me so earnestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Milady have an unpleasant life because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come up with a way to repay the debt soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, I need to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:22.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the meaning behind my life yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.21,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, it's about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.18,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:31.60,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Ha... Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:10.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you from anyone who tries to make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:23.32,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:24.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.54,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:29.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:41.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:50.22,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is going to become\Na battle anime starting next episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.60,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:21:04.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The boy lets go of his hesitation\Nand finds meaning in protecting his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Where is butler Hayate's future?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:11.22,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll fight against many issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.70,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose that pendant, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.97,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.98,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Maria's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:23.93,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.36,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.71,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any cash off of you, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:31.72,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, how do you plan on going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.54,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's up there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.05,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,They left me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:49.21,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,What a cold, cruel world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:30.90,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:31.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.29,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:37.87,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, today's the last day for Maria's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:39.53,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, that character's finally showing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:46.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Would that happen to be the person\Nwho ranked 1st in the popularity ranking, Hina-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:47.97,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.85,0:23:52.70,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun, it'll be Nagi from next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:56.06,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But considering this is my last chance,\Naren't I being rather badly mistreated?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:23:59.48,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.24,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're Hayate-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:03.26,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:05.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's been since Christmas we last met. What were you doing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:10.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot has happened, and I'm working as a butler at a certain mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:11.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that supposed to be a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I got to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:15.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:17.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Hayate no Gotoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:21.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We Were Once Taught by the Space Police That Youth is to Not Look Back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:25.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But Hayate-kun, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to see a new type of conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.68,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,SFX: Swooooosh....
